#| "selecting <guilabel>Never</guilabel>."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Show Favorite Folders View</guilabel> section allows you to "
"change how your favorite folders are displayed. <guilabel>As Icons</"
"guilabel> uses a lot of space, so if you have several favorite folders you "
"might try <guilabel>As List</guilabel>. If you do not care about favorite "
"folders you can disable this feature altogether by selecting "
"<guilabel>Never</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"La sección <guilabel>Mostrar vista de carpetas favoritas</guilabel> le "
"permite cambiar como su carpeta de favoritos muestra su carpeta favorita. "
"<guilabel>Como iconos</guilabel> usa mucho espacio, por lo que si dispone de "
"varias carpetas favoritas podría intentar <guilabel>Como lista</guilabel>. "
"Si no tiene ninguna carpeta favorita, puede desactivar la vista "
"seleccionando <guilabel>Nunca</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1079
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "On by default, <guilabel>Folder Tooltips</guilabel> display additional "
#| "information like the total number of messages, unread messages and "
